commit.title: [warnings] Disable warning 59 [assignment to a non-mutable value] to make flambda happy.
commit.message:
[warnings] Disable warning 59 [assignment to a non-mutable value] to make flambda happy.

See issue #8043.

Using `[@@@ocaml.warning "-59"]` to disable this fails, it seems like
an OCaml bug.
